com.taobao.datax.engine.plugin
类 BufferedLineExchanger

java.lang.Object
  com.taobao.datax.engine.plugin.BufferedLineExchanger
所有已实现的接口：
LineReceiver, LineSender
public class BufferedLineExchanger
extends java.lang.Object
implements LineSender, LineReceiver

A buffer handler used by Reader to write data into Storage or by Writer to read data from Storage.

This class has two faces, when it works with reader, it shows its LineSender face. when it works with Writer, it shows its LineReceiver face. Both faces have used Buffering mechanism to work well.
